00:06:49.629 --> 00:06:51.069
&gt;&gt; KITAGAWA: Yeah.
&gt;&gt; SHEEHAN: And being in the showcase.

00:06:51.069 --> 00:06:53.029
&gt;&gt; Thank you for coming.
&gt;&gt; KITAGAWA: Definitely, and so, thank you

00:06:53.029 --> 00:06:58.979
very much.
&gt;&gt; Great, thanks for the good time and that

00:06:58.979 --> 00:06:58.990
